ConScapeRtools 0.4.11
---------
* Integrated documentation and API refinements
* Added repository automation guidance in `AGENTS.md`
* Ignored the development-only `examples/` directory for Git tracking
* Promoted `distance_scale` in `tile_design()` output while retaining `exp_d` for backwards compatibility
* Clarified examples and vignette guidance for affinities, tiled runs, sensitivity workflows, and manual mosaicking
* Updated tests for the expanded `tile_design()` return object

ConScapeRtools 0.4.10
---------
* Added ConScape-aligned API helpers for inspecting input slots and configuring sensitivity analyses
* Generalized `run_conscape()` arguments for source qualities, target qualities, affinities, cost functions, connectivity functions, metrics, and sensitivity outputs
* Added Julia runner support for additional ConScape metrics and sensitivity outputs when available in the installed Julia package
* Expanded package documentation for tiled workflows, ConScape slot mapping, movement affinity inputs, and sensitivity interpretation
* Added a detailed user guide vignette
* Extended tests for API normalization, sensitivity specifications, plotting, and Julia wrapper argument handling

ConScapeRtools 0.4.9
---------
* Increased unit test coverage above 75 percent
* Added mocked tests for Julia wrappers, `tile_design`, and `run_conscape`
* Added additional tests for CRS handling, invalid inputs, plotting, and tile IDs
* Filtered single-raster ConScape outputs to raster files when reading results

ConScapeRtools 0.4.8
---------
* Cleaned package metadata and documentation for CRAN compatibility
* Added unit tests for tiling, validation, masking, and mosaicking workflows
* Fixed distributed Julia batch script lookup
* Updated raster helper calls and S3 registration to satisfy package checks

